description:
Vol Special

Sociopolitical Documentary hosted by Fernand Melgar, published by TV5Monde in 2011 - French narration. 
http://docuwiki.net/images/6/60/Vol-Special-Cover.jpg

Information
------------------------------
Special flights.

The men at Frambois detention centre Switzerland are held there awaiting deportation. Some of them have lived in the country for several years, working, paying taxes, starting families. Their incarceration can last up to 18 months. Behind the closed doors of prison, tensions are rising day by day.
